{"tid":817571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"領略了一條職場生存之道","createTime":"2018-09-13T12:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T14:00:06.000Z","uid":164163,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"32dff6ee05789f88f63c9c48e256e13b2d2b9975","tid":817571,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:35:56.000Z","msg":"做嘢要醒爬 積極用心 唔好怕蝕底呢啲講到口都臭 <br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得最緊要嘅就係唔好俾人入到位<br />\n打個比喻:  我有個同事每朝返工打卡嗰陣 都係俾原定返工嘅時間早7分鐘 所以佢就諗住放工嗰陣可以早7分鐘走 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以佢今日俾個阿頭照咗一輪肺 鬧鳩佢第一日出嚟做嘢啊?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家覺得又點睇? 有冇啲自己嘅心得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9cb204b94d1f90872f40f0c08e957e743463d90","tid":817571,"uid":70532,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:37:03.000Z","msg":"冇用架 要入你點都有位入"},{"pid":"51fdc94f48cb8ab48525bad510bacf045740067e","tid":817571,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:37:30.000Z","msg":"第一日出黎做嘢呀？"},{"pid":"db1bfdef6d86c8afde2f735ce743c15f15ef36c6","tid":817571,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9cb204b94d1f90872f40f0c08e957e743463d90","tid":817571,"uid":70532,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:37:03.000Z","msg":"冇用架 要入你點都有位入"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"ching 點解咁卑觀?"},{"pid":"df63de29fa19ed4d4770e70fe0bf18a11c45c77f","tid":817571,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51fdc94f48cb8ab48525bad510bacf045740067e","tid":817571,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:37:30.000Z","msg":"第一日出黎做嘢呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:38:24.000Z","msg":"阿頭!?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d393d7a52fc1fc455d55879588f0f7eeaf4c33da","tid":817571,"uid":62020,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c9cb204b94d1f90872f40f0c08e95